<li><a href="#AI-tools-for-SEO-research">AI tools for SEO research</a></li>
</ul>
<p><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/16.0.1/72x72/2753.png" alt="‚ùì" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> Want to know what 300 agencies think about pricing, services, and challenges? Download our free <a href="https://marketing.localiq.com/WSLIQContentDLWebsite2023AgencyIndustryReport.html?cid=Web_Blog_InContent_TextLink_StateoftheAgency2023_Download&amp;utm_source=wordstream&amp;utm_medium=web&amp;utm_campaign=2023SOTA&amp;utm_content=compare_pricing&amp;utm_term=Web_Blog_InContent_TextLink_StateoftheAgency2023_Download&amp;utm_source=wordstream&amp;utm_medium=blog&amp;utm_campaign=incontent_links&amp;utm_content=2023SOTA">State of the Digital Marketing Agency report</a>.</p>
<div id="What-are-the-benefits-of-an-AI-marketing-tool-for-your-marketing-agency"></div>
<h2>What are the benefits of an AI tool for your marketing agency?</h2>
<p>Every <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/pay-per-click-agency">marketing agency</a> can <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ai-in-marketing">use AI</a> to its advantage. Here are a few ways it can help yours.</p>
<h3>Brainstorm ideas</h3>
<p><a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/best-ai-tools">AI writing tools</a> and search engines can spark new ideas for your marketing content and campaigns.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2023/05/08/chatgpt-prompts">Prompt an AI tool</a> with questions like, ‚ÄúWhat are 20 B2B pain points companies face in the [input] industry?‚Äù. Or try, ‚ÄúGive me 50 campaign ideas to attract new customers in the [input] industry.‚Äù</p>
<p>While you have to verify accuracy and weigh different ideas, it‚Äôs a great starting point to get in a creative flow.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-prompt.webp" alt="AI tools for marketing agency: Screenshot of a prompt and response from ChatGPT." width="936" height="600" class="aligncenter wp-image-80946 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-prompt.webp 936w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-prompt-480x308.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 936px, 100vw" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><em>In this example, I type a question into ChatGPT, and it gives me 20 blog topic ideas to help brainstorm future articles.</em></p>
<h3>Automate repetitive tasks</h3>
<p>AI <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/how-to-promote-your-digital-marketing-agency">marketing agency</a> tools help reduce predictable tasks. Whether hitting publish or transferring an inbound marketing piece to WordPress, you can save hours with efficient automation.</p>
<p>You can save precious hours you would have spent doing grunt work and instead use them to strengthen your marketing strategy and produce more materials.</p>
<h3>Reach new markets</h3>
<p>AI platforms can identify <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2023/08/04/customer-segmentation-models">audience segments</a> you hadn‚Äôt thought of before. You can also reach more markets by automating your process and easily repurposing different content mediums for new platforms.</p>
<p>Many opportunities exist to reach new markets with impressive research and content creation tools.</p>
<h3>Reduce avoidable human error</h3>
<p>Using the power of machine learning and AI, marketing AI tools can identify and correct errors before your clients see them.</p>
<p>A tool like Grammarly, for example, can correct grammar and spelling errors and improve phrasing automatically. AI is a great option that helps the marketing team be more productive while avoiding common issues.</p>
<h3>Save on costs</h3>
<p>Whether you need to save on production value with videos or crank out first drafts of social media content, there are plenty of areas where you can save time, labor, and money on daily marketing tasks.</p>
<p>That gives you and your team more time and energy to focus on the most essential, important tasks.</p>
<p>Now that we know the benefits of AI marketing agency tools, let‚Äôs review some of the best ones.</p>
<p><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/16.0.1/72x72/1f4a1.png" alt="üí°" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> Want more? <strong>Get your free <a href="https://marketing.localiq.com/WSLIQContentDLWebsiteAIinMarketingGuide.html?cid=Web_Any_BlogInContent_PPC_AIMarketing_Download">guide to AI in marketing</a></strong> and see how you should and shouldn‚Äôt use this revolutionary technology.</p>
<h2>Top AI tools for your marketing agency</h2>
<p>Most AI marketing tools are built for a specific purpose, like writing new copy or automating a workflow. That‚Äôs how we‚Äôve categorized this list, based on the primary challenge each tool tackles.</p>
<div id="AI-tools-for-content-creation"></div>
<h3>AI tools for content and copy creation</h3>
<p><a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ai-copywriting-tools">AI copywriting tools</a> have received the most spotlight in <a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2022/08/24/technology/ai-technology-progress.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">recent years</a>. That‚Äôs helped fuel the creation of innovative <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2023/06/05/generative-ai-in-digital-marketing">generative AI</a> tools with a growing list of useful features.</p>
<p>Since content isn‚Äôt all copy, we‚Äôve included platforms that help you create and edit video and image assets, too.</p>
<h4>1. ChatGPT</h4>
<p><a href="https://chat.openai.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ChatGPT-3.5</a> and ChatGPT-4 (Open AI continues to create new versions) have led the AI writing craze by offering one of the most accessible copywriting tools.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-chatgpt.webp" alt="AI tools for marketing agency - ChatGPT homescreen. " width="870" height="600" class="aligncenter wp-image-80947 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-chatgpt.webp 870w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-chatgpt-480x331.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 870px, 100vw" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://chat.openai.com/auth/login" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Source</em></a></p>
<p>The platform is excellent for brainstorming. If you‚Äôre working on an email newsletter, social media campaign, or blog article, you can ask for ideas, outlines, lists, and many other starter materials to help you save time.</p>
<p>Some marketing agencies use it for content development, though there are <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2023/06/28/ai-for-marketing">risks in trusting</a> its accuracy. Plus, the output often feels ‚ÄúAI-written.‚Äù But it‚Äôs a great trusty sidekick to get projects started and boost your marketing efforts.</p>
<p><strong>Pricing:</strong> ChatGPT-3.5 is free to use, ChatGPT-4 starts at $20 per month.</p>
<h4>2. Jasper</h4>
<p><a href="http://jasper.ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Jasper</a> is another great AI writing solution built for teams and creative workflows.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-jasper.webp" alt="AI tools for marketing agency - Jasper homescreen." width="847" height="600" class="aligncenter wp-image-80948 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-jasper.webp 847w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-jasper-480x340.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 847px, 100vw" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.jasper.ai/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Source</em></a></p>
<p>You can efficiently work with the platform for quick project creation and execution. The tool offers <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ai-prompts-for-social-media">prompts</a> and automates the ‚Äúhuman‚Äù part of AI writing by incorporating your brand voice.</p>
<p>The tool also helps you write more factually (compared to ChatGPT) and on-brand.</p>
<p><strong>Pricing:</strong> Plans start at $59 a month (billed annually).</p>
<h4>3. Copy.ai</h4>
<p>An alternative to Jasper, <a href="http://copy.ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Copy.ai</a> helps marketing teams automate blog briefs, create copy (like scraping URLs for AI ad copy), and accelerate other writing tasks.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-copyai.webp" alt="AI tools for marketing agency - Copy.ai homescreen." width="846" height="600" class="aligncenter wp-image-80949 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-copyai.webp 846w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-copyai-480x340.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 846px, 100vw" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.copy.ai/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Source</em></a></p>
<p>Copy.ai has many prompts and tools to help guide your writing queries for better results.</p>
<p><strong>Pricing:</strong> Copy.ai is free to use with limited words. Upgrade to unlimited words for $36 monthly (annual plan).</p>
<h4>4. LocaliQ&#8217;s Google Ads AI Copy Tool</h4>
<p>For being so short, Google Ads are mighty tough to write sometimes. You either get stuck in the rut of using the same words, or you just don&#8217;t have time. That&#8217;s where LocaliQ&#8217;s <a href="https://localiq.com/google-ads-ai-copy-tool/?cid=Web_LiQ_InContent_AICopyTool_AICT&amp;itm_source=localiq&amp;itm_medium=blog&amp;itm_campaign=incontent_links" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Ads AI Copy Tool</a> comes in. You just feed it a little information about your business, target keywords, industry, etc., and it creates both Google Ads headlines and ad descriptions.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/google-ads-ai-copy-tool-wordstream-screenshot.webp" alt="AI tools - screenshot of the Google Ads AI Copy Tool." width="749" height="862" class="aligncenter wp-image-89926 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/google-ads-ai-copy-tool-wordstream-screenshot.webp 749w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/google-ads-ai-copy-tool-wordstream-screenshot-480x552.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 749px, 100vw" /></p>
<p>The tool gives you 10 variations of both headlines and descriptions so you can pick which you like the best.</p>
<p><strong>Pricing:</strong> 100% free.</p>
<h4>5. Typeframes</h4>
<p>This clever AI tool creates videos in just a few minutes. If you want to advertise a new product or create buzz for an event, <a href="https://www.typeframes.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Typeframes</a> is the platform for you.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-typeframe.webp" alt="AI tools for marketing agency - Typeframes homescreen." width="854" height="600" class="aligncenter wp-image-80950 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-typeframe.webp 854w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-typeframe-480x337.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 854px, 100vw" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.typeframes.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Source</em></a></p>
<p>Easily type a few words, and the tool automatically makes a video. You can add music, animations, images, and other effects. It‚Äôs a great way to ship new ideas and campaigns with a fraction of the time and money you‚Äôve spent in the past.</p>
<p><strong>Pricing:</strong> Typeframes starts at $24 monthly (on the annual plan).</p>
<h4>6. Midjourney</h4>
<p><a href="https://www.midjourney.com/home" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Midjourney</a> is designed to make image creation easy.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-midjourney.webp" alt="AI tools for marketing agency - Midjourney homescreen." width="819" height="600" class="aligncenter wp-image-80951 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-midjourney.webp 819w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-midjourney-480x352.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 819px, 100vw" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.midjourney.com/home?callbackUrl=%2Fexplore" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Source</em></a></p>
<p>Using Midjourney, marketing agencies can make stunning, cinematic-style artwork that looks detailed and eye-catching. You can generate any style image in seconds. Whether it‚Äôs a realistic photo of customers enjoying your client‚Äôs offering with emotional benefits, a painting, or cartoon-style artwork, Midjourney will spin it up with a couple of prompts.</p>
<p>Midjourney can help save on specific stock photo needs or even give your design team a head start on a campaign.</p>
<p><strong>Pricing:</strong> The platform starts at $8 monthly (billed annually).</p>
<h4>7. Grammarly</h4>
<p><a href="http://grammarly.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Grammarly</a> is an editing tool that spots and corrects your grammar and spelling errors. And its AI additions help you create content, too.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-grammarly.webp" alt="AI tools for marketing agency - Grammarly home screen. " width="816" height="600" class="aligncenter wp-image-80952 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-grammarly.webp 816w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-grammarly-480x353.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 816px, 100vw" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.grammarly.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Source</em></a></p>
<p>Use Grammarly to find awkward phrasings and passive sentences. It‚Äôll also help you reword copy for a better read. The addition of generative AI gives Grammarly the power to suggest new ways to write existing text or help you start writing something completely new.</p>
<p>The platform is a must, and it will save you lots of time (and embarrassing moments like that one time you spelled ‚Äúexpresso‚Äù instead of ‚Äúespresso‚Äù).</p>
<p><strong>Pricing:</strong> Grammarly is free to use (with upgraded plans available).</p>
<div id="AI-tools-for-social-media-management"></div>
<h3>AI tools for social media management</h3>
<p><a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2022/01/11/most-popular-social-media-platforms">Social media</a> is one of the fastest-moving components of marketing. Your clients need you to publish often, engage with their followers, and <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2018/07/20/social-listening">listen</a> for trends and consumer needs. It‚Äôs not an easy job, so AI tools are pivotal to helping automatize and strengthen your agency‚Äôs strategy.</p>
<p>These tools automate repetitive <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/social-media-marketing">social media marketing</a> tasks so you can achieve greater returns for your clients.</p>
<h4>8. FeedHive</h4>
<p><a href="https://www.feedhive.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">FeedHive</a> started as a scheduling and publication tool, but has since invested in powerful AI features to make <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/february-blog-ideas">social media content</a> creation better and easier.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-feedhive.webp" alt="AI tools for marketing agency -FeeHive home screen. " width="854" height="600" class="aligncenter wp-image-80953 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-feedhive.webp 854w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-feedhive-480x337.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 854px, 100vw" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.feedhive.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Source</em></a></p>
<p>Now the platform helps you create new posts and get them published faster.</p>
<p>FeedHive‚Äôs AI collects <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2020/10/07/agency-profitability-metrics">analytics</a> so you can get more information on your results. The platform also provides an AI chat assistant built on GPT technology. It helps with social media performance predictions and suggestions (like suggesting the <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/best-time-to-post-on-social-media">best time to post</a>).</p>
<p><strong>Pricing:</strong> FeedHive offers an agency plan for multiple clients at $239 a month (billed annually).</p>
<h4>9. Hootsuite OwlyWriter AI</h4>
<p><a href="https://www.hootsuite.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hootsuite</a> is an early entrant in the social media management space, and it‚Äôs recently evolved to add AI capabilities.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-owelywriter.webp" alt="AI tools for marketing agency - OwlyWriter AI home screen." width="936" height="600" class="aligncenter wp-image-80954 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-owelywriter.webp 936w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-owelywriter-480x308.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 936px, 100vw" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.hootsuite.com/platform/owly-writer-ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Source</em></a></p>
<p>For example, Hootsuite‚Äôs OwlyWriter AI is designed to quickly create captions and generate post ideas for all your accounts and segments. It‚Äôs a great way to utilize Hootsuite‚Äôs winning social media technology with a built-in writer‚Äîall in one place.</p>
<p><strong>Pricing:</strong> OwlyWriter AI is free for a limited time to Hootsuite users.</p>
<h4>10. Lately.ai</h4>
<p><a href="http://lately.ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Lately.ai</a> creates social media posts from your existing content.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-lately.webp" alt="AI tools for marketing agency - Lately.ai home screen." width="936" height="554" class="aligncenter wp-image-80955 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-lately.webp 936w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-lately-480x284.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 936px, 100vw" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.lately.ai/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Source</em></a></p>
<p>It‚Äôs hard to develop great social media content consistently. But what if I were to say you and your clients already have hundreds of social media posts hiding in the middle of all the other content you‚Äôve created?</p>
<p>Lately.ai pulls all that dormant content from existing web pages, articles, documents, and ebooks. Then it uses AI to turn long-form assets into social media copy so you can publish more relevant and valuable posts with less effort.</p>
<p><strong>Pricing:</strong> Lately.ai offers plans based on your number of social channels, with its first package starting at $49 monthly.</p>
<div id="AI-tools-for-automation"></div>
<h3>AI tools for automation</h3>
<p>One of the best use cases for AI is streamlining operational tasks and <a href="https://www.link-assistant.com/news/top-search-engines.html">monitoring success</a>. Below are a few great platforms to improve key parts of your process.</p>
<h4>11. HubSpot Breeze AI</h4>
<p>Tasks like generating and repurposing content, writing prospecting emails, and setting up reports can take a lot of valuable time and effort. <a href="https://www.hubspot.com/products/artificial-intelligence#below-header-breeze_wf_header_splash" target="_blank" rel="noopener">HubSpot‚Äôs Breeze AI</a> simplifies these tasks (and a lot more!).</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/hubspot-breeze-ai.webp" alt="hubspot breeze ai tool" width="875" height="413" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-87065" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/hubspot-breeze-ai.webp 875w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/hubspot-breeze-ai-480x227.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 875px, 100vw" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.hubspot.com/products/artificial-intelligence#below-header-breeze_wf_header_splash" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Source</em></a></p>
<p>With this AI tool, you can pick between numerous ‚ÄúBreeze Agents‚Äù‚Äîthink of them as chatbots specialized in specific departments‚Äîto automate particular workflows. For example, the Content Agent is useful for generating and repurposing landing pages, blog posts, or any other type of content.</p>
<p>Meanwhile, the Social Media Agent streamlines social media management-related tasks. It can deliver content and ideal posting time suggestions, generate network-specific posts, and even suggest social campaign ideas based on your business details and previous social performance.</p>
<p><strong>Pricing: </strong>You can get started with Breeze AI for free.</p>
<h4>12. Wordable</h4>
<p>Transferring content from Google Docs to a CMS like WordPress can take thousands of hours and dollars. Between formatting posts and <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/seo-content-beginners-guide" target="_blank" rel="noopener">optimizing them for SEO</a>, publishing content is a huge time sink. <a href="https://wordable.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Wordable</a> does it in one click.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-wordable.webp" alt="AI tools for marketing agency - Wordable home screen." width="936" height="553" class="aligncenter wp-image-80956 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-wordable.webp 936w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-wordable-480x284.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 936px, 100vw" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://wordable.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Source</em></a></p>
<p>The platform takes your Google Docs to WordPress, HubSpot, and Medium. It retains your format, headers, and HTML elements. The app saves you time, so you can focus on publishing more content.</p>
<p><strong>Pricing:</strong> Wordable offers a limited plan for free. The paid plan is $50 a month.</p>
<h4>13. Zapier</h4>
<p><a href="https://zapier.com/l/home?utm_source=google&amp;utm_medium=cpc&amp;utm_campaign=gaw-usa-nua-search-desktop-brand-long_tail&amp;utm_adgroup=brand_workflow_automation&amp;utm_term=zapier%20automation&amp;utm_content=9009942&amp;gad_source=1&amp;gclid=EAIaIQobChMI3_2Iiee_hAMV0kl_AB3yJw2sEAAYASAAEgIPtPD_BwE" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Zapier</a> is a no-code solution that automates almost any repetitive task.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-zapier.webp" alt="AI tools for marketing agency - Zapier home screen." width="933" height="600" class="aligncenter wp-image-80957 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-zapier.webp 933w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-zapier-480x309.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 933px, 100vw" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://zapier.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Source</em></a></p>
<p>It works by connecting different platforms with APIs so they work together. If you start a new Word doc for each client project, then create an event in Asana, and generate a bill in an accounting tool, Zapier will link those platforms so it all happens as soon as you create the Word doc.</p>
<p>It‚Äôs a great platform for building your own AI solution as you face many predictable actions in your marketing agency.</p>
<p><strong>Pricing:</strong> Zapier has a limited free plan with the option to upgrade, starting at $19.99 monthly (billed annually).</p>
<h4>14. Taskade AI</h4>
<p>If you need a great marketing project management tool, this might be for you. <a href="https://www.taskade.com/?via=start&amp;fp_sid=1-g-EAIaIQobChMIsr-ptee_hAMVzTbUAR1gPg3_EAAYASAAEgJVdvD_BwE&amp;gad_source=1&amp;gclid=EAIaIQobChMIsr-ptee_hAMVzTbUAR1gPg3_EAAYASAAEgJVdvD_BwE" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Taskade AI</a> generates task lists and mind maps. It also helps you set up agendas and workflows‚Äîall with AI.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-taskade.webp" alt="AI tools for marketing agency - Taskade home screen." width="896" height="600" class="aligncenter wp-image-80958 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-taskade.webp 896w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-taskade-480x321.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 896px, 100vw" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.taskade.com/ai/app" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Source</em></a></p>
<p>You can collaborate in your workplace and even utilize in-app AI assistance. It‚Äôs project management and strategy empowered by AI technology.</p>
<p><strong>Pricing:</strong> The platform starts at $19 monthly (billed annually).</p>
<div id="AI-tools-for-chatbots"></div>
<h3>AI tools for chatbots</h3>
<p>If you‚Äôre looking for a way to connect with clients on your agency website or onboard them for your app or portal, these AI solutions will help.</p>
<h4>15. Drift</h4>
<p>The <a href="https://www.drift.com/platform/conversational-marketing/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Drift</a> app is great for communicating with your clients and prospects 24/7. The B2B chatbot uses Drift technology called Conversational AI, which automates conversations.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-drift.webp" alt="AI tools for marketing agency - Drift home screen." width="936" height="575" class="aligncenter wp-image-80959 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-drift.webp 936w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-drift-480x295.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 936px, 100vw" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.drift.com/platform/conversational-marketing/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Source</em></a></p>
<p>The platform is designed to improve your sales pipeline to get more clients. The one downside is that it can be costly, but if it benefits your clients directly (or your agency), the revenue it generates might be worth it.</p>
<p><strong>Pricing:</strong> Drift starts at $2,500 monthly.</p>
<h4>16. HelpHub by CommandBar</h4>
<p><a href="https://www.helphub.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">HelpHub</a> is another AI chat solution that learns from your resources, marketing website, content, and more to answer visitor queries on your agency website.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-helphub.webp" alt="AI tools for marketing agency - HelpHub home screen." width="819" height="600" class="aligncenter wp-image-80960 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-helphub.webp 819w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-helphub-480x352.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 819px, 100vw" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://helphub.commandbar.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Source</em></a></p>
<p>You can equip your clients and prospects with 24/7 assistance powered by AI technology and trained by your documentation.</p>
<p><strong>Pricing:</strong> The starter plan is $249 monthly.</p>
<h4>17. Perplexity</h4>
<p>The <a href="https://www.perplexity.ai/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Perplexity</a> AI search platform is handy for content marketing research. You can get it as a browser extension and ask questions as you work on a piece.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-perplexity.webp" alt="AI tools for marketing agency - perplexity home screen." width="926" height="600" class="aligncenter wp-image-80961 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-perplexity.webp 926w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-perplexity-480x311.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 926px, 100vw" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://chromewebstore.google.com/detail/perplexity-ai-companion/hlgbcneanomplepojfcnclggenpcoldo" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Source</em></a></p>
<p>The bot answers you with multiple citations so you can verify the information, dig deeper, and link to sources if necessary (that‚Äôs a big win for AI writing!).</p>
<p>The app offers unique answers and resources that help you save time and escape a jam.</p>
<p><strong>Price:</strong> Perplexity is free to use. Users can also upgrade to the Pro plan at $20 a month.</p>
<div id="AI-tools-for-SEO-research"></div>
<h3>AI tools for SEO research</h3>
<p>Research is the foundation of any successful SEO strategy. Here are the top tools you can use for your agency.</p>
<p><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/16.0.1/72x72/1f44b.png" alt="üëã" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> Finding the perfect keywords is a snap with our free <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/keywords?cid=Web_Any_InContentTextLink_Keywords_KWTool">Keyword Tool</a>.</p>
<h4>18. Keyword Insights</h4>
<p><a href="https://www.keywordinsights.ai/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Keyword Insights</a>‚Äô AI technology identifies thousands of keyword ideas, puts them into <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/topic-clusters-for-local-seo">topic clusters</a>, and helps you create content.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-keyword-insights.webp" alt="AI tools for marketing agency - Keyword Insights home page." width="936" height="578" class="aligncenter wp-image-80962 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-keyword-insights.webp 936w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-keyword-insights-480x296.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 936px, 100vw" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.keywordinsights.ai/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Source</em></a></p>
<p>It‚Äôs a great automated tool for research, but it also helps you plan and outline your strategy. When you are ready to produce content, you click a button, and the information and brief go right to your content writer.</p>
<p><strong>Pricing:</strong> The basic plan starts at $58 a month.</p>
<h4>19. Clearscope</h4>
<p><a href="https://www.clearscope.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Clearscope</a> uses AI technology to identify competing website pages and their common keywords, then analyzes your content for comparison. This can shave hours off the time you spend on each piece.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-clearscope.webp" alt="AI tools for marketing agency - Clearscope home screen." width="936" height="456" class="aligncenter wp-image-80963 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-clearscope.webp 936w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-clearscope-480x234.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 936px, 100vw" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.clearscope.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Source</em></a></p>
<p>With Clearscope, you input your content and improve your chance of showing up on search engines by adding the suggested keywords and enhancing the piece using a graded scale.</p>
<p><strong>Pricing:</strong> Plans start at $199 monthly.</p>
<h4>20. Frase.io</h4>
<p><a href="https://www.frase.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Frase</a> does a great job combining SEO research with AI writing. In short, you can do everything in one place to research, outline, write, and optimize your content.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-frase.webp" alt="AI tools for marketing agency - Frase home screen." width="936" height="552" class="aligncenter wp-image-80964 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-frase.webp 936w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/ai-tools-for-marketing-agency-wordstream-frase-480x283.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 936px, 100vw" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.frase.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Source</em></a></p>
<p><strong>Pricing:</strong> Subscribers pay $12.66 monthly (billed annually) with options to upgrade packages.</p>
<h2>Choosing the right AI marketing agency tools in 2025</h2>
<p>Effective marketing AI tools help you save resources and increase productivity to build better campaigns and strategies. You just have to find the right fit.</p>
<p>It‚Äôs best to start with a challenge and work backward. Where are the workflow bottlenecks? What repetitive busywork is a creative contributor constantly bogged down by? Then, look for AI tools that address those challenges. Do that regularly, and you‚Äôll run an even more efficient marketing agency.</p>
<p>Here are the best AI tools for marketing agencies:</p>
<ol>
<li>ChatGPT</li>
<li>Jasper</li>
<li>Copy.ai</li>
<li>Google Ads AI Copy Tool</li>
<li>Typeframes</li>
<li>Midjourney</li>
<li>Grammarly</li>
<li>FeeHive</li>
<li>Hootsuite OwlyWriter AI</li>
<li>Lately.ai</li>
<li>HubSpot Breeze AI</li>
<li>Wordable</li>
<li>Zapier</li>
<li>Taskade AI</li>
<li>Drift</li>
<li>HelpHub</li>
<li>Perplexity</li>
<li>Keyword Insights</li>
<li>Clearscope</li>
<li>Frase.io</li>
</ol>
